  "remarks": "Valeriy Pakhnits is the former Russian-appointed acting head of the administration of the Starobilskyi district. In his role, he supervised the seizure of Ukrainian agricultural products and grain for their transfer to Russia. He is therefore responsible for, supporting and implementing actions or policies, which undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
